Nigerian-American writer, Tomi Adeyemi who is the author of the fantasy novel Children of Blood and Bone earlier today took Twitter to call out famous author, Nora Roberts. Adeyemi who expressed her displeasure with Roberts shared a photo of the cover of her book and the cover of Robert’s new book which share similar titles. Nora’s new fantasy novel is titled, Of Blood and Bone, a phrase she has used very often in her books. Tomi, on her Twitter, wrote:  In an update, however, Adeyemi has issued an apology after revealing that Roberts reached out to her and explained that she’d never actually heard of her own book before the Twitter call out. Read her update below: 